## ðŸš€ Quick Start

### Access the API:
- Base URL: `https://your-app.onrender.com`
- Health Check: `GET /api/home/health`
- All Products: `GET /api/products`
- Categories: `GET /api/products/categories`

### API Documentation:
- Swagger UI: `/swagger-ui/`
- H2 Database Console: `/h2-console`

